<section class="py-20 md:py-28">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4">
    <div class="fade-in mb-16 text-center">
      <h2 class="mb-4 text-3xl font-bold text-white md:text-4xl">
        <span data-i18n="problem.title.1">GitHub Copilot costs $10/month.</span><br />
        <span class="text-kobi-muted" data-i18n="problem.title.2">In USD.</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="mx-auto max-w-2xl text-lg text-kobi-muted" data-i18n="problem.subtitle">
        For most Bangladeshi developers, that's not just expensive — it's
        inaccessible.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-3">
      <div class="fade-in rounded-xl border border-kobi-border bg-kobi-surface p-8">
        <div class="mb-4 text-4xl">🚫</div>
        <h3 class="mb-2 text-xl font-semibold text-white" data-i18n="problem.1.title">No international card</h3>
        <p class="leading-relaxed text-kobi-muted" data-i18n="problem.1.desc">Most Bangladeshi developers don't have a Visa/Mastercard that works internationally. GitHub Copilot requires one.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="fade-in rounded-xl border border-kobi-border bg-kobi-surface p-8">
        <div class="mb-4 text-4xl">💸</div>
        <h3 class="mb-2 text-xl font-semibold text-white" data-i18n="problem.2.title">$10 = ৳1,100/month</h3>
        <p class="leading-relaxed text-kobi-muted" data-i18n="problem.2.desc">That's expensive for junior devs and students in Bangladesh. Kobi starts at ৳500 — less than half the cost.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="fade-in rounded-xl border border-kobi-border bg-kobi-surface p-8">
        <div class="mb-4 text-4xl">🤷</div>
        <h3 class="mb-2 text-xl font-semibold text-white" data-i18n="problem.3.title">No local support</h3>
        <p class="leading-relaxed text-kobi-muted" data-i18n="problem.3.desc">When things break, you're on your own. Kobi is built for BD developers with local support and BDT billing.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
